name: [badbro]-sexy underwear
description:
I wanted to make sexy underwear, body suits, and net stockings.

If you know how to express the stockings in the checkpoints you are using, you should be able to get decent results with very light intensity.

Recommended settings and triggers are listed below.

weight : <lora:badbronunderwear:0.4>

triggers : fishnets, lingerie, see-through, bodysuit, pantyhose, bare shoulders, halter neck

If you properly combine the triggers, different shapes of underwear come out.

Confirmed that it mixes with other lora without any sense of incongruity
